ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectAdministrator of Government of Newfoundland and Labrador 1) The Hon. David B. Orsborn- October 21-24, 2011 and October 26-29, 2011 and 2) The Hon. Gale Welsh - November 1-4, 2011.
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of NEWFOUNDLAND AND LABRADOR (1) the Honourable DAVID B. ORSBORN from October 21-24, 2011, inclusive, and from October 26-29, 2011, inclusive; and (2) the Honourable B. GALE WELSH from November 1-4, 2011, inclusive.
